There is one more reason that most of you have overlooked that a Newbie ( I really HATE that term..lol ) might see that you don't. I have to tell you a few things about me for this to make sense. age - over 20, sex - female. Now this may seem trivial but the game seems to be over run with males with an extreme testosterone overload. I have noticed that the mage classes seem to attract a more patient and mature person than the hack and slash trades.<br>
This may easily be because of the time and patience needed to create a good character. most younger guys trying to get their ya ya's out will change to something more instantly gratifying at a low level.<br>
So in closing, Don't sell yourselves short in the personality dept. The mages I've met so far just reinforce my choice to join the class.<br>
<br>
